definition: variant of 凋謝|凋谢[diao1 xie4]
to thank/to apologize/to wither (of flowers, leaves etc)/to decline

sentences.english: When that shall vade, by verse distills your truth.
sentences.chinese: 當韶華雕謝，詩提取你的純精。

sentences.english: For at a frown they in their glory die.
sentences.chinese: 一蹙額便足雕謝他們的榮華。
